<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>OpenGL pre-3.0: Set the same blend state for all draw buffers OpenGL 3.0-pre4.0: Set the same blend state for all draw buffers, but can disable blending for particular buffers OpenGL 4.0+: Can set blend state individually for each draw buffer.</db:para>
</db:section>
