<db:title>bufferIndex : int</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the index of the Draw Buffer that this <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-blendequationarguments.xml">BlendEquationArguments</db:link> applies to. If negative, this will apply to all Draw Buffers.</db:para>
